Package org.opentosca.toscana.plugins.kubernetes.docker.mapper

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseImageMapper
    Allows the mapping of OsCapabilities (from a tosca model) to a docker base image.
    BaseImageMapperConfiguration
    This configuration is used to Configure the BaseImageMapper It enables Scheduling and supplies the BaseImageMapper with a list of BaseImageTypes it should look for

    MapperUtils
